README FILE FOR BRIGHTNESS CONTROL USING HAND GESTURE… 
1.	Open the file
2.	Install necessary libraries (mediapipe, cv2, numpy, brightnesscontrolmodule, etc.) using the command “pip install ‘#########’ ”
3.	‘########’ is the name of library.
4.	After installing, run the main file.
5.	A pop-up window will appear on the screen with the webcam turned on.
6.	Using two fingers to control the brightness.
7.	If the distance between the fingers increases, the brightness will increase else decrease.
8.	After attaining the required brightness, stop the program.
